Create the Second Resource Group (if needed):
az group create --name RG2 --location spaincentral

Create the Second Virtual Network (On-Premises Simulation VNet):
az network vnet create \
  --resource-group RG2 \
  --name OnPremVNET \
  --address-prefix 10.1.0.0/16 \
  --location spaincentral

Create Subnet for the On-Premises Simulation VNet:
az network vnet subnet create \
  --resource-group RG2 \
  --vnet-name OnPremVNET \
  --name OnPremSubnet \
  --address-prefix 10.1.1.0/24
